data.description: This End Unit Townhome Shows Like a Model & With Lush Green Trees Lining the Private Backyard - It's Your Low-Maintenance Oasis! This Home Is Better Than New & FULL of Upgrades - Crown Molding, LVP Flooring Throughout First Floor - Blinds & Curtain Rods, Granite Counters & White Cabinets, Patio & an Almost Fenced In Backyard! Open Concept Floorplan With Lots of Windows & Light! Stainless Steel Appliances - Refrigerator Included! HUGE Owners Suite Has a Nice Sitting Area, BIG Walk-In Closet, & a Walk-In Shower. Guest Bedrooms Are Spacious & Bright. The Backyard Has a Storage Area, Patio, & Gorgeous View. The One Car Garage & Double Driveway Allow For Plenty of Parking! Flowers Plantation is a Premier Community With Walking Trails, Pools & Fitness Centers Available, Shopping, Restaurants, & So Much More!
